<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[259, 297, 765, 336]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[132, 352, 512, 390]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[260, 441, 549, 470]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[260, 514, 444, 580]]<|/det|>
